OL,7,FSix people have admitted to affray
OL,8,Fover escalting violence in Newcastle
OL,9,Fwhich resulted in the death of 14-year-
OL,10,Fold Gordon Gault.
OL,12,FThe teenager was stabbed in the arm in
OL,13,FElswick in November 2022 but died in
OL,14,Fhospital six days later.
