OL,7,FSix people have now all pleaded guilty
OL,8,Fto affray at Newcastle Crown Court,
OL,9,Fincluding 18-year-old Jack Hardy, 18-
OL,10,Fyear-old Raymond Matthew and 28-year-
OL,11,Fold Liam Thompson. The remaining three
OL,12,F17-year-old boys cannot be named for
OL,13,Flegal reasons.
OL,15,FAll of the defendants will be
OL,16,Fsentenced at a later date.
