OL,7,FDetective Chief Inspector Matt Steel,
OL,8,FNorthumbria Police, said: "The truly
OL,9,Fdevastating impact of violence is
OL,10,Fclear for all to see with the tragic
OL,11,Fdeath of Gordon and our thoughts very
OL,12,Fmuch continue to be with his loved
OL,13,Fones.
OL,15,F"Gordon was killed after an escalating
OL,16,Fdispute culminated in violence, with
OL,17,Ftwo teenagers subsequently being
OL,18,Fconvicted of his manslaughter.
