OL,7,F"We have seen a group of people admit
OL,8,Ftheir part in the disgraceful disorder
OL,9,Fwhich occurred the evening Gordon, who
OL,10,Fwas the youngest person present, was
OL,11,Ffatally wounded."
OL,13,FHe added: "Violence destroys lives and
OL,14,Fhas absolutely no place in our
OL,15,Fcommunities.
