OL,7,F"As a Force, we are committed to
OL,8,Freducing the impact of this type of
OL,9,Foffending. This includes targeting
OL,10,Fthose who carry weapons and working
OL,11,Fwith our partners to prevent incidents
OL,12,Fby educating people about the dangers
OL,13,Fand consequences of doing so.
OL,15,F"Our message to anyone who does pick
OL,16,Fup a weapon or involves themselves in
OL,17,Fviolence remains very simple ` think
OL,18,Fagain. We urge people, to make that
OL,19,Fchoice today."
