OL,4,Cescalating violence that resulted in
OL,5,Cboy's death
OL,7,FLast month Carlos Neto, 18, of
OL,8,FSalford, and Lawson Natty, 18, of
OL,9,FNewbiggin Hall, who denied murdering
OL,10,FGordon, were convicted of manslaughter
OL,11,Ffollowing a trial at Newcastle Crown
OL,12,FCourt.
OL,14,FThey were also found guilty of
OL,15,Fwounding with intent to commit
OL,16,Fgrievous bodily harm in relation to a
OL,17,Fsecond victim, who suffered an injury
OL,18,Fto his back.
OL,20,FCarlos Neto admitted wounding Gordon
OL,21,Fbut claimed it was in self-defence.
